milestones.description: Andy Flower and Heath Streak's 130-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 91 between Andy Flower and Guy Whittall
Andy Flower and Heath Streak's 130-run partnership is the highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 124 between Rashid Latif and Mohammad Yousuf
This is the highest match aggregate (526) involving teams England & Zimbabwe in ODIs
